211
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:08,440
and techniques, which we'll talk about. What 
do you think? Is that a good response to the-

212
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:12,480
I'm sold. I don't need a job, but 
I want to join one. You also just  

213
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:16,480
had a really beautiful way of describing 
