00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:50,000
candidate market fit. So here's the thing, and 
this is why this is so important in a down market,  

244
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:55,720
when you're looking for a job, you're 
in a marketplace with supply and demand  

245
00:20:55,720 --> 00:21:00,880
characteristics. So if there's a lot of supply, 
which there is right now in the tech world because  

246
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:07,160
there's been a lot of layoffs, the overall 
economy, there's been net job additions,  

247
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:11,160
