264
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:44,320
at the very low end of the national average. 
So this is not a slow down, take two years,  

265
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:50,760
whatever. No, no. Most people need to put food 
on the plate, so it's a slow down at first. And  

266
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:54,040
we as product people should understand this. 
You want to think about your strategy. You want  

267
00:22:54,040 --> 00:22:58,440
to understand the marketplace, your customer, the 
