312
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:50,320
the listening tour is find colleagues, friends, 
people that are other, say, product managers and  

313
00:26:50,320 --> 00:26:54,320
get their feedback on what you want, what you 
don't want, what you hate, what your goals are.

314
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:56,960
And what they're seeing in the market, 
