00:26:56,960 --> 00:27:00,360
I see. Got it. So it's like, "Oh, this is 
unrealistic. You're not going to get this."

316
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:00,800
That's right.

317
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:01,640
Looking for that [inaudible 00:27:02]-

